<Equipment>

<!-- Valid <Params> attributes:
	roundsPerSecond			- required
	audibleSoundRadius		- required, in meters
	physicsImpactForce		- required, only affect hit objects
	
	numPellets				- optional, overrides weapon default number of pellets
	accuracyAdd 			- optional, default 0
	accuracyMultiplier 		- optional, default 100 - In percents. Multiplies final accuracy amount ( after scopes, attack types and accuracyAdd are applied )
	silenced				- optional, default 0 - Set to 1 for silent shooting
	overpenetrates			- optional, default 0 - Set to 1 will make shots pierce first hit human
	damageType				- optional, default 0 - Can be changed for rare modding reasons to fake more powerful weapons
 -->
 
